			<footer class="comment-meta">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
					<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/76c6deb48809e922082ef3f5001cd3a9?s=68&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-68 photo' height='68' width='68' /><span class="fn">Wendy Young</span> on <a href="http://wildtruth.net/32-reasons-why-the-schizophrenogenic-mother-concept-is-incorrect/#comment-911"><time datetime="2014-02-01T08:58:03+00:00">February 1, 2014 at 8:58 am</time></a> <span class="says">said:</span>
									</div><!-- .comment-author .vcard -->

				
