      My second son, Yeshe( who is schizophrenic), developed this during the yr after his brothers death. Culminating in hanging himself on the anniversary of Morgans death. His father found him in time, and revived him. But he sustained some mild brain injury( short term memory loss).<br />
      He was on medication, we with help of Drs took him off. But he had another episode/ meds again/  another episode/ different meds. Hard core meds. Now, several yrs later , he&#8217;s stable. Relationship with his father has broken down. His father has moved away. I&#8217;m his carer.<br />
