			<div class="comment-content"><p>dear Dolma,<br />
this is a very intense message from you.  i am wishing you the best.  how to proceed?  aaaah!!  i wish there were an easy answer.  if there were an easy answer i would probably say &#8212; just keep growing and healing your own inner traumas to the best of your ability&#8230;.  same advice i give myself&#8230;&#8230;.  but often in my experience life&#8217;s answers aren&#8217;t so easy in practical terms&#8230;..<br />
this essay&#8230;..yes&#8230;..a tough one.  for years i didn&#8217;t have it linked from my website&#8217;s main page so it was hard to find&#8230;&#8230;.because it was a tough one.  but now&#8230;.well&#8230;&#8230;.i linked it.  i don&#8217;t want to offend people, yet i also want, to some degree, to state my point of vew.<br />
wishing you the best,<br />
daniel</p>
</div>

